own to <LOCATION> Rangoon </LOCATION> aboard <LOCATION> Burmese </LOCATION> military aircraft. Seventy-six students returned Thursday, bringing to 260 the number who have returned under the program, <LOCATION> Thai </LOCATION> officials said.
