<HEAD>Fatal Crashes of Military Aircraft</HEAD>
<HEAD>With AM-Germany-Crash</HEAD>
<DATELINE>BREMEN, West Germany (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
 Crashes involving military aircraft have killed 103 people in <LOCATION> West </LOCATION> <LOCATION> Germany </LOCATION> within the last year. Here is a list:
</TEXT>
