<HEAD>New England's Biggest Utility Offers $2 Billion for PSNH</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By WENDY MITMAN</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>MANCHESTER, N.H. (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
